{"tid":1471633,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"唔好忘記我地有隻捉鬼遊戲叫做：三國殺","createTime":"2019-08-14T10:18:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T09:41:12.000Z","uid":216800,"like":59,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"3cb9ba66108a8d6c8b00aaa09a18d42b3bc16202","tid":1471633,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:18:28.000Z","msg":"哩隻係一隻七情上臉 專玩口術嘅遊戲<br />\n六個玩家<br />\n一個主公<br />\n兩個忠臣<br />\n一個內奸<br />\n二個反賊<br />\n<br />\n無人知對方身分 但六個人都會一齊講：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">忠臣呀主公！</span></span><br />\nA：屌你老味孫權都扮忠臣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nB：嘩！阿公 咁樣同你講野wo！哩條友非忠即奸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nC：阿公！我見到佢猴住你兩粒桃！你小心佢呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nD：阿公！我以表忠誠，你打我，我唔會打返你！<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nE：嘩！你條撚樣，咁撚樣出賣自己都得既！你睇佢！賊眉賊眼，我係你就殺咗佢先，少個人少雙筷！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n主公：...嘩屌 咁多忠臣既！打一打你先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無錯，就係一隻咁既遊戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係話訓練大家點去捉鬼，係訓練大家喺大是大非嘅情況下，點樣保持冷靜去做出判定。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df875086537fbbc33a9affc38b566ee435e30b70","tid":1471633,"uid":280648,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:23:52.000Z","msg":"通常我玩嗰陣第一個死係內奸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7de6f764aae715dfd58a6b99dc5fc9bada9f8c2c","tid":1471633,"uid":216800,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"df875086537fbbc33a9affc38b566ee435e30b70","tid":1471633,"uid":280648,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:23:52.000Z","msg":"通常我玩嗰陣第一個死係內奸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:26:30.000Z","msg":"要睇大家演技好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我果班個個拎過奧斯卡咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0425241249ad1fc9d0392dd611ec28750c3a4c80","tid":1471633,"uid":46459,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:30:20.000Z","msg":"通常打內奸打得最出力嘅係內奸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca0672b4b9e69d9abe2a87338ba8c55803dfe679","tid":1471633,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:30:45.000Z","msg":"人狼遊戲先岩"},{"pid":"d814c4de94de8e577b07336732823b85f25c6229","tid":1471633,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:31:05.000Z","msg":"人狼遊戲先似"},{"pid":"c050318cd3e5162c284bdd07772e521ee44b8e82","tid":1471633,"uid":216800,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0425241249ad1fc9d0392dd611ec28750c3a4c80","tid":1471633,"uid":46459,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:30:20.000Z","msg":"通常打內奸打得最出力嘅係內奸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:33:34.000Z","msg":"內奸乜人都搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bbaaab2e621edb3827c8812b3f09f77764a2bec","tid":1471633,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d814c4de94de8e577b07336732823b85f25c6229","tid":1471633,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:31:05.000Z","msg":"人狼遊戲先似"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:34:25.000Z","msg":"未玩過，可唔可以介紹下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fce96bb34ed8635dc99ca7275f99e4c5d458a3d1","tid":1471633,"uid":32401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:36:19.000Z","msg":"Wrong wo,內奸係兩邊到幫喎"},{"pid":"2d8acfadc8e3e8f2e3c600c645bc81e04d1cd6a8","tid":1471633,"uid":32401,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:36: